# Frontend Configuration
# ======================

# Base URL for the backend API (no trailing slash)
# For local dev: http://localhost:8000/api
# For production: https://your-backend.onrender.com/api
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL="http://localhost:8000/api"

# URL for the backend Socket.io server
# For local dev: http://localhost:8000
# For production: https://your-backend.onrender.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_SOCKET_URL="http://localhost:8000"

# Note: On Vercel, set these environment variables in the Vercel dashboard
# to point to your production backend URL.
